				</ORIGINAL-REFEX>
			</REFERENCE>
			<STRING> can be approached from two mountain refuges:* The refuge du Promontoire at 3,082 metres, is situated at the bottom of the steep south buttress of the peak, and allows access to routes on the south face of  </STRING>
